### ─────────────────────────────────────────────
### HelpRest API
### Compatible: VS Code REST Client + Insomnia
### ─────────────────────────────────────────────

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

# After running "Login", copy the accessToken to this variable:
@accessToken = PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
###  HEALTH CHECK
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health
Content-Type: application/json

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
###  AUTH
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

### Register User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teste User",
  "email": "teste@email.com",
  "password": "senha123",
  "birthDate": "1995-06-15"
}

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "joao@teste.com",
  "password": "teste123"
}

### Refresh Token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
###  USER
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

### Get My Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Update Profile
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "name": "João Atualizado",
  "socialLinksEnabled": true,
  "socialLinks": {
    "instagram": "@joao.teste"
  }
}

### Update User Flags
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/users/me/flags
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "flagIds": []
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
###  FLAGS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

### List All Flags
GET {{baseUrl}}/flags
Content-Type: application/json

### Create Flag
POST {{baseUrl}}/flags
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "type": "dietary",
  "identifier": "sugar-free",
  "description": "Estabelecimento com opções sem açúcar",
  "tag": "Sem Açúcar",
  "backgroundColor": "#E2B93B",
  "textColor": "#FFFFFF"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
###  ESTABLISHMENTS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

### List Establishments
GET {{baseUrl}}/establishments?page=1&limit=5
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Single Establishment
GET {{baseUrl}}/establishments/REPLACE_WITH_ID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Recommended (Curitiba centro)
GET {{baseUrl}}/establishments/recommended?lat=-25.429&lng=-49.27&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Get Nearby (5km, Curitiba centro)
GET {{baseUrl}}/establishments/nearby?lat=-25.429&lng=-49.27&maxDistance=5000&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Search Establishments
GET {{baseUrl}}/establishments/search?q=vegano&page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### Create Establishment
POST {{baseUrl}}/establishments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "companyName": "Novo Restaurante Teste",
  "location": {
    "state": "PR",
    "city": "Curitiba",
    "neighborhood": "Centro Cívico",
    "address": "Rua Teste, 123",
    "coordinates": { "lat": -25.42, "lng": -49.27 }
  },
  "flagIds": [],
  "logo": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512621776951-a57141f2eefd?w=200&h=200&fit=crop"
}

### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════
###  VISITS
### ═══════════════════════════════════════════════

### Create Visit
POST {{baseUrl}}/visits
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "establishmentId": "REPLACE_WITH_ID",
  "rating": 5,
  "review": "Excelente restaurante! Opções veganas deliciosas."
}

### List User Visits
GET {{baseUrl}}/visits/user/REPLACE_WITH_USER_ID?page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### List Establishment Visits
GET {{baseUrl}}/visits/establishment/REPLACE_WITH_ID?page=1&limit=10
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
